      "type": "note",
      "id": "bYNZJ",
      "x": 0,
      "y": 740,
      "name": "Note — expanded",
      "width": 280,
      "height": 0,
      "content": "EXPANDED: header label left, gradient '+ New' affordance right -> navigates to /dashboard/chat/new. Mirrors dashboard '+ New conversation' button. Persistent (does not vanish like the empty-state 'Start one' CTA)."
    },
